  "subject": "Fix basic_vm_macro cleanup race condition",
  "commit_message": "Fix basic_vm_macro cleanup race condition\n\n- basic_vm and basic_vm_macro tests were using the same customer\n- both test clean up (delete) that customer once they are done\n- if both tests are running in parallel, then this behaviour\n  causes issues\n- make sure that both tests operate with their own customer\n\nIssue-ID: INT-2370\nChange-Id: Ia35cc6f6da2e070ee42e591fb5d9d97c8f5eeb6a\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
